scenes.description: Iofi is drawing Ankimo on an easel while talking to Tokino Sora.
Iofi reveals the finished drawing of Ankimo.
Iofi finishes the drawing and Sora promises to display it.
Iofi introduces her guests from hololive ID Gen 2 and 3: Kureiji Ollie, Vestia Zeta, and Kobo Kanaeru.
Zeta gives the first hint for the guessing game: "Amis" (Fishy).
